随着新冠肺炎疫情的蔓延，在过去的一天，韩国、意大利、伊朗等多国新增确诊数继续上升，中国以外累计确诊病例超过15000例。
Over the past day, the number of new cases confirmed in South Korea, Italy and Iran has continued to rise, with more than 15,000 confirmed cases outside China.
世卫组织：部分国家对新冠肺炎准备不足当地时间3月5日，世卫组织在日内瓦召开新冠肺炎疫情例行发布会，介绍全球疫情情况。
WHO: Some countries are under-prepared for pneumonia on March 5, the World Health Organization in Geneva convened a routine briefing on the global outbreak of pneumonia.
世卫组织总干事谭德塞表示，部分国家对新冠肺炎不够重视，准备不足，且疫情蔓延至更多国家，尤其是卫生系统较弱的国家面临病毒威胁，令人担忧。
WHO Director-General Lindsey said some countries are not paying enough attention to pneumonia, are ill-prepared, and the spread of the epidemic to more countries, especially those with weak health systems, is a cause for concern.
但谭德塞同时指出，目前全球115个国家未上报任何新冠肺炎病例，有21个国家仅出现一例。
But he said 115 countries did not report any new cases of pneumonia, with only one case reported in 21 countries.
过去14天内，有5个出现新冠肺炎病例的国家没有上报新增病例。
In the past 14 days, no new cases were reported in five countries with new cases of pneumonia.
这些国家和中国的经验均表明，疫情发展不是不可逆转的。
The experience of both those countries and China shows that the epidemic is not irreversible.
谭德塞呼吁，新冠肺炎对所有国家都是威胁，各国政府应协调所有部门，采取迅速行动应对新冠肺炎。
Tamerlane called for new crown pneumonia to be a threat to all countries, and governments should coordinate all sectors and take swift action to respond to pneumonia.
韩国确诊超6千 庆山被定为传染病特别管理地区韩国中央防疫对策本部5日通报，截至5日下午4时，韩国较当天0时新增新冠肺炎确诊病例322例，累计确诊病例达6088例。
South Korea has confirmed 322 new cases of pneumonia in 2006, bringing the total number of confirmed cases to 6,088, the ministry said Wednesday.
韩国政府5日宣布，考虑到庆尚北道新冠肺炎最近新增病例主要集中在庆山市，决定将该市列为传染病特别管理地区。
The city of Gyeongshan has been designated as a special management area for infectious diseases, taking into account that the latest cases of the disease are concentrated in the city, the government said Tuesday.
韩国方面称，目前庆山市内已出现二代感染和小规模聚集性感染，有必要在社区感染进一步扩散前集中采取措施遏制疫情向其他地区蔓延。
South Korea said the city has emerged second-generation infections and small-scale aggregation of infection, there is a need to focus on community infection before further spread measures to curb the spread of the epidemic to other regions.
庆山市位于庆尚北道南部，其西面、南面分别与大邱市和庆尚北道清道郡接壤。
Qingshan City is located in the southern Gyeongshan Province, its west, south and Daegu City and Qingdao County Gyeongshan North Province, respectively.
3月4日，在韩国大邱庆北大学医院，医护人员转送患者。
March 4, at Daegu Qingbei University Hospital, South Korea, medical staff transferred patients.
新华社发（李相浩摄）此前，由于出现大规模聚集性感染事件，大邱市和庆尚北道清道郡于2月21号被韩国政府指定为传染病特别管理地区。
Xinhua News Agency said the city of Daegu and Ching Tao county in Gyeongshan province were designated as special areas for infectious diseases by the South Korean government on February 21 because of mass-infection outbreaks.
意大利累计确诊3858例 政府拨款75亿欧元用于应对疫情当地时间3月5日18时，意大利民防部门负责人、新冠病毒应急委员会专员安杰洛·博雷利在例行疫情新闻发布会上表示，意大利现存新冠病毒感染肺炎病例为3296例，较前一日增长590例；死亡病例148例，较前一日增长41例；治愈病例414例，较前一日增长138例。
Italy confirmed 3,858 cases with 7.5 billion euros local time The head of Italy's civil defence agency and Commissioner of the New Crown Virus Emergency Response Committee, Angelo Borelli, said at a routine news conference that 3,296 cases of IRAV infection had been reported, 590 more than the previous day, 148 deaths had been reported, 41 more than the previous day, and 414 cases had been cured.
该国目前累计新冠肺炎确诊病例达3858例。
The cumulative number of confirmed cases of pneumonia in the country now stands at 3,858.
5日，意大利西北部的瓦莱达奥斯塔大区首次报告两例病例，这也标志着该国20个大区已全部出现了新冠肺炎确诊病例。
On 5 May, two cases were reported for the first time in the Valleda Osta region of north-western Italy, which also marked the emergence of confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia in all 20 regions of the country.
在同一天，意大利总理孔特宣布，政府拨款75亿欧元用于支持该国的家庭以及企业应对疫情带来的紧急状况。
On the same day, Prime Minister Conte announced that the Government had allocated 7.5 billion euros to support families and businesses in the country to respond to the emergency created by the epidemic.
意大利布雷西亚医务人员在医院外搭建的帐篷中工作。
Medical workers in Brescia, Italy, work in tents set up outside the hospital.
图/新华社伊朗累计确诊3513例学校将停课至20日根据伊朗卫生部最新消息，当地时间5日，伊朗新增新冠肺炎确诊病例591例，新增死亡15例。
Iran has confirmed 591 new cases of pneumonia and 15 new deaths in the country, Xinhua news agency said Wednesday.
截至到当天中午，伊朗累计确诊新冠肺炎病例3513例，其中739例康复，107例死亡。
By noon of the same day, 3,513 new cases of pneumonia had been confirmed in Iran, of which 739 had recovered and 107 had died.
据伊朗塔斯尼姆通讯社5日消息，伊朗议长国际事务顾问侯塞因·谢赫伊斯兰因患新冠肺炎去世。
Iran's Speaker of Parliament, international affairs adviser Hussein Sheikh, has died of pneumonia, Iran's Tasmanian news agency said Monday.
伊朗卫生部部长表示，目前已经做出两个重要决定：一个是组建30万个疫情排查小组；另一个是所有大中小学及教育机构停课至3月20日。
Iran's health minister says two important decisions have been made: one to form 300,000 outbreak detection teams and the other to close all schools, colleges and universities and educational institutions until March 20.
3月2日，在伊朗德黑兰，一名女子戴着口罩出行。
On March 2, a woman walks in a mask in Tehran, Iran.
又一艘邮轮！美国“至尊公主”号出现疫情美国加州卫生部官员4日表示，当天该州出现的首例死亡病例此前曾乘坐“至尊公主”号邮轮。
The first case of death in the US state was aboard the USS Princess Supreme, health officials said Thursday.
目前，这艘轮船正在驶往旧金山途中，据称船上已有21人出现感染症状。
The ship is now en route to San Francisco and 21 people on board are reported to have contracted the infection.
美国疾控中心已要求和该患者有过接触的62名乘客留在自己的房间内，等待检测。
The CDC has asked 62 passengers who had been in contact with the patient to stay in their rooms pending tests.
加州政府命令该船不得入港，将派遣应急人员登船检测。
The state government ordered the ship not to enter the port and will send emergency personnel on board for inspection.
这艘邮轮正被困海上，船上共有3000多名乘客和船员。
The ship was stranded at sea with more than 3,000 passengers and crew on board.
此前，已有两名乘坐过该邮轮的乘客确诊新冠肺炎，其中一人死亡。
Two passengers aboard the vessel have been confirmed to have pneumonia, one of whom died.
目前，当地卫生官员已开始对船上人员进行检测。
Local health officials have begun testing people on board.
“至尊公主号”和“钻石公主号”都隶属于全球最大的度假公司嘉年华集团。
Both the Princess Supreme and the Princess are affiliated with Carnival, the world's largest holiday company.
该集团总部位于美国佛罗里达州。
The group is headquartered in Florida, USA.
报告称全美至少有197起确诊病例当地时间3月5日，美国有线电视新闻网（CNN）报道，田纳西州出现首例确诊新冠病毒感染者。
At least 197 cases confirmed nationwide March 5 (CNN) reported the first confirmed case of the new crown virus in Tennessee, CNN reported.
当地时间3月5日下午，纽约州州长科莫召开发布会，称当天在纽约再确诊多例新冠病毒感染者，目前纽约州确诊病例总数已达到22例。
NEW YORK (Reuters) - The governor of New York State has confirmed a number of new cases of the virus in New York City, bringing the total number of confirmed cases to 22, New York State time said Monday.
根据约翰•霍普金斯大学汇编的数据，全美至少有197起确诊病例。
According to data compiled by Johns Hopkins University, there are at least 197 confirmed cases nationwide.
当地时间4日，由于受到新冠病毒威胁，美国加州州长宣布该州进入紧急状态。
California's governor declared a state of emergency Thursday after being threatened by the new Crown virus.
加州目前是全美第三个宣布进入紧急状态的州。
California is now the third state in the country to declare a state of emergency.
当地时间3月5日，美国参议院通过了一项83亿美元的紧急拨款法案，以帮助抗击新冠肺炎疫情。
On March 5, the United States Senate passed a $8.3 billion emergency funding bill to help fight the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic.
这一法案现在已交美国总统特朗普，预计他将很快签署这项法案。
The bill has now been handed over to US President Trump, who is expected to sign it soon.
受到美国国内新冠病毒感染病例持续上升的影响，美国股市在当地时间5日出现大幅下跌，截至当天收盘，道琼斯工业平均指数、纳斯达克综合指数、标普500指数均下跌超过百分之三，其中道琼斯指数大跌近1000点，跌幅3.6%。
The Dow Jones Industrial Average, the Nasdaq Composite Index and the S & P 500 all fell more than 3 percent by the end of the day, with the Dow Jones Industrial Average falling nearly 1,000 points, or 3.6 percent, as a result of the continuing rise in new crown infections in the U.S.
德国确诊病例升至500例法国确诊病例升至423例据《欧洲时报》德国当地时间3月5日17时公布的统计数据，截至3月5日17时，德国已累计确诊新冠肺炎患者500例。
The number of confirmed cases in Germany rose to 423, with 500 confirmed cases in Germany as of 17: 00 on March 5, the European Times said.
当地时间3月5日晚间，法国卫生部最新通报，截至当天，法国累计确诊新冠肺炎病例达423例，较前一天增长138例，其中23人情况危殆。
A total of 423 new cases of pneumonia have been confirmed in France, up 138 from the previous day, 23 of them critically, the Health Ministry said on the night of March 5.
3月5日当天新增死亡病例3例，总计死亡病例7例。
On 5 March, there were three new deaths and a total of seven deaths.
多国累计确诊病例超过百例瑞士：截至当地时间5日6点，瑞士共确诊新冠肺炎病例111例，其中一人死亡，3人治愈。
More than 100 cases were diagnosed in Switzerland: 111 cases of pneumonia were confirmed in Switzerland, one of them dead and three cured, as of 6: 00 local time.
新加坡：新加坡卫生部5日晚上发布文告，当天新增5例新冠肺炎确诊病例，累计确诊117例。
SINGAPORE (Reuters) - Singapore's Ministry of Health announced Sunday that it had confirmed 117 new cases of pneumonia on Sunday.
出院人数累计81人，另有7例危重。
A cumulative total of 81 people were discharged, with seven others in critical condition.
英国：据英国疾控部门5日公布的最新数据，英国境内新冠病毒感染者新增29人，总确诊人数累计达 116人。
NEW YORK (Reuters) - A total of 116 new cases have been confirmed in the UK with 29 new cases of the virus, according to the latest figures released by the CDC on Friday.
在伦敦附近的雷丁，一名在本地感染新冠病毒的年迈患者死亡。
In Reading, near London, an elderly patient infected with the new crown virus died.
这也是英国境内首起死亡病例。
It was also the first death in Britain.
南非发现首例新冠肺炎确诊病例据当地媒体报道，南非卫生部长兹韦利·穆凯兹3月5日发表声明，南非发现首例新冠病毒检测呈阳性的病例。
South Africa Finds First Confirmed Case of New Crown Pneumonia South Africa's health minister, Zweli Mukezi, said in a statement on March 5 that South Africa had found its first positive case of the new crown virus.
目前，患者家属以及其他的接触者也将被隔离和检测。
Family members and other contacts will now also be quarantined and tested.
据了解，这名患者是一名38岁男子，从意大利返回南非后确诊。
The patient is believed to be a 38-year-old man diagnosed after returning to South Africa from Italy.
